"title": "4404: food",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4404",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture contains references to varied foodstuffs, which comprised the diet of the people of the Near East in biblical times.</p>\n<h2>God made provision for food in creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:29-Gen1:30\">GEN 1:29–1:30</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Flour</h2>\n<h3>Flour the main ingredient in bread</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:6\">GEN 18:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:2\">EXO 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:19\">JDG 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:24\">1SA 28:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:33\">MAT 13:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:21\">LUK 13:21</a></p>\n<h3>Flour figured largely in the staple diet</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:12-1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:12–17:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:27-2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:27–17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:22-1Kgs4:23\">1KI 4:22–4:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:41\">2KI 4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:1\">2KI 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:16\">2KI 7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:40\">1CH 12:40</a></p>\n<h3>Fine flour more refined and more expensive than the common variety</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:13\">EZK 16:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:19\">EZK 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:13\">REV 18:11–18:13</a></p>\n<h3>Flour in grain offerings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:1-Lev2:10\">LEV 2:1–2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:14-Lev6:23\">LEV 6:14–6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:8-Lev14:11\">LEV 14:8–14:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:11-Num5:15\">NUM 5:11–5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:13-Num6:15\">NUM 6:13–6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:1-Num15:4\">NUM 15:1–15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:9\">NUM 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num29:7-Num29:11\">NUM 29:7–29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:29\">1CH 23:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:14\">EZK 46:14</a></p>\n<h3>Flour in other offerings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:11\">LEV 5:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:1-Exod29:3\">EXO 29:1–29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:22-Exod29:25\">EXO 29:22–29:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:12\">LEV 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:25-Lev8:28\">LEV 8:25–8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:15-Lev23:17\">LEV 23:15–23:17</a></p>\n<h2>Honey</h2>\n<h3>Honey a sweet delicacy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:11\">GEN 43:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:31\">EXO 16:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:13\">DEU 32:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:8-Judg14:9\">JDG 14:8–14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:25-1Sam14:26\">1SA 14:25–14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:27-2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:27–17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:1-1Kgs14:3\">1KI 14:1–14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:31-2Kgs18:32\">2KI 18:31–18:32</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:10\">19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:103\">PSA 119:103</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:13-Ps81:16\">PSA 81:13–81:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:11\">SNG 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:1\">SNG 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:22\">ISA 7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer41:8\">JER 41:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:13\">EZK 16:13</a></p>\n<h3>The promised land described as flowing with milk and honey</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:7-Exod3:8\">EXO 3:7–3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:17\">EXO 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:5\">EXO 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:3\">EXO 33:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:24\">LEV 20:24</a>NUM <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:27\">13:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:8\">NUM 14:8</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:12-Num16:14\">NUM 16:12–16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:3\">DEU 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:8-Deut11:9\">DEU 11:8–11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:9\">DEU 26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:20\">DEU 31:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:6\">JOS 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:22\">JER 32:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:6\">EZK 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:15\">EZK 20:15</a></p>\n<h3>Prohibition against burning honey on the altar</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:11\">LEV 2:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Raisins</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:1\">2SA 16:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:1-Num6:4\">NUM 6:1–6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:18\">1SA 25:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:11-1Sam30:12\">1SA 30:11–30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:19\">2SA 6:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:3\">1CH 16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:40\">1CH 12:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:5\">SNG 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:1\">HOS 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>Lentils</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:29-Gen25:34\">GEN 25:29–25:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:27-2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:27–17:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:11-2Sam23:12\">2SA 23:11–23:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:1-Ezek4:10\">EZK 4:1–4:10</a></p>\n<h2>Cheese</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:17-1Sam17:18\">1SA 17:17–17:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:27-2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:27–17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:8-Job10:11\">JOB 10:8–10:11</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should not eat food offered to idols</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:19-Acts15:20\">ACT 15:19–15:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:25\">ACT 21:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:1-1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:1–8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14\">REV 2:14</a></p>",
